node.text: So excited to announce that I’m officially a @vitacoco #RealPartner!!!!!!! You know me, and how I actually drink Vita Coco Pressed every day PERIOD. I also really really love that Vita Coco supports coconut farming communities in the Philippines🇵🇭we have something really special dropping this Thursday on World Coconut Day. 🌴🥥I’m not going to say much more right now… but something cute is coming. Go to @vitacoco on IG and TikTok to get a peek at what we have planned for this week and who knows maybe you’ll even see me in the stores one day 😏🌴🥥
